{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <i>The Legend of Kuro</i>, you play as Kuro, a samurai frog seeking vengeance after demons mercilessly destroyed his village. This 2D platformer will test your skills with precise controls and unique mechanics, such as dashing through orbs and enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kuro's journey spans 50 meticulously crafted levels, filled with escalating challenges, enemies inspired by Japanese mythology, and epic boss encounters like the Oni of Chains and the Shogun Oni.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Between each stage, Kuro returns to the Rising Sun Village, a sanctuary filled with memorable characters who deepen his story of loss, determination, and honor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With striking visuals and an atmospheric soundtrack, <i>The Legend of Kuro</i> delivers a compelling narrative, intense challenges, and a unique artistic style for an unforgettable experience.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3462720/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739487678","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3462720/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1739487678","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3462720/ae7100eb45059068d6bbfa9b7ce13d25c7dd335e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739487678","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3462720/ae7100eb45059068d6bbfa9b7ce13d25c7dd335e/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739487678","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"The Legend of Kuro contains stylized violence, including combat with swords and other melee weapons. The game features blood effects, but no realistic gore or dismemberment. There are no sexual themes, drug use, or self-harm in the game."},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <i>The Legend of Kuro</i>, you play as K